%!
% Ghostscript PDF/A definition file
% OutputIntent uses sRGB ICC profile in the same directory as this file.

% Tell GS where to find the ICC (we pass full path via -sOutputICCProfile too; harmless redundancy)
[/ICCProfile (sRGB2014.icc)
 /OutputConditionIdentifier (sRGB)
 /Info (sRGB IEC61966-2.1)
 /RegistryName (http://www.color.org)
] setdistillerparams
